305191938.name: Double Crisis
305191938.description: Two teams of villains emerge from their hideouts to clash over the fate of the world in Pokémon TCG: Double Crisis! Inside special 7-card booster packs, you'll discover incredible Team Aqua and Team Magma Pokémon. Get ready for danger, get ready for trouble—get ready for Double Crisis!
